{"operationName":"paymentListInquiry","variables":{"inquiry":{"transactionType":"PAYMENT","pageNumber":1,"pageSize":7,"pageInfo":{"transactionTypeSubCategories":[{"paymentStatusCode":"COMPLETE","nextDateFetchKey":""}]}}},"query":"fragment ActivityFields on ZellePayment {
  messageReference
  isCancellable
  paymentAmountSplit {
    linkedPaymentAmount
    splitRequestedAmount
    splitTotalAmount
    __typename
  }
  payeeAccountToken
  payeeId
  payeeName
  payeePartyName {
    firstName
    lastName
    __typename
  }
  payerAccountName
  payeeAccountName
  payeeAccountAliasId
  payerAccountAliasId
  payerId
  payerName
  paymentAuxStatus
  paymentDirection
  paymentMemo
  paymentPurpose
  paymentReference
  paymentSchedule {
    scheduleId
    nextPaymentDate
    frequency
    scheduleDay
    otherDay
    hasRecurringAutoPayment
    stopBy
    maximumAmount: maximumTransactionAmount
    maximumTransactionCount
    __typename
  }
  paymentStatus
  paymentType
  transferAmount
  transferAmountCurrency
  transferDate
  valueDate
  lastUpdatedDate
  __typename
  transactionSource
  transactionTypeCode
  rejectionReason
  payerAccountToken
  deliverySpeed
  transactionReference
}

query paymentListInquiry($inquiry: ZellePaymentInquiryRequest) {
  inquiry: zellePaymentListInquiry(
    appName: ZELLE
    zellePaymentInquiryRequest: $inquiry
  ) {
    activities: payments {
      ...ActivityFields
      __typename
    }
    pageInfo {
      transactionTypeSubCategories {
        paymentStatusCode
        nextDateFetchKey
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    additionalTransactions
    totalPages
    pageSize
    pageNumber
    totalRecords
    __typename
  }
}
"}
